          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/384_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> to a <strong>blender</strong> (or pan if using a <strong>(stick) blender</strong>) – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Set aside until later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
