    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your<strong> mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Roughly chop the<strong> drained mozzarella</strong></p><p>Grate your<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped mozzarella </strong>and<strong> grated cheese</strong> in the reserved bowl and season with<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
