    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the tray of<strong> </strong>roasted vegetables<strong> </strong>from the oven, then add them to the tomato stock</p><p>Add in your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Blitz together until smooth, then add the <strong>blitzed soup</strong> to a pan over a medium heat and cook for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Serve in bowls and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and plenty of <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>warming pepper soup</strong></p>",
