      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> cheese melt[s]</strong> into thirds lengthways – these are your <strong>cheese melt soldiers</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>cheese melt soldiers </strong>alongside the <strong>warming pepper soup</strong></p><p>Drizzle the soup with <strong>olive oil </strong>and season generously with<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
